E002.description1: The Italian State successfully kills hopes of Venetian Independence by crushing the rebellion.

E001.description: Today, the Italian people choose a new parliament. The election is tightly fought, and very likely will decide the fate of Italy in the near future.  Whom will the Italian people choose?
E001.title: The General Election
